text.tspan: Benjamin Gibson is an emerging graphic designer
constantly on the lookout for new ways to learn
and improve his craft. Whilst studying graphic
design as a senior at George Mason University,
Ben has developed a fascination of digital art
and all that it encompasses. As an intern at CO2
Productions Ben has worked on professional
projects for business expos, schools, and
summer camps. Ben’s freelance work includes
tattoo designs and logos for friends and family.
Ben is hoping to strengthen his skills in the Adobe
Creative Cloud while working with a progressive
and cutting-edge company. Ben can be reached
